,"The big flat buttons on the handset have large lettering and numbering. This can help those with large fingers or impaired motor skills to dial accurately.","This phone set comes with a one-year warranty from the manufacturer. Clarity can answer your questions or concerns directly via telephone or email. You can also hop on to the website and read the company’s FAQs page and download the instruction manual."]},"id":"0575acf6-e50e-432f-bd35-c50d710e27db","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"b00987e6-1903-4231-813b-2112403d876b","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Clarity’s E814CC cordless phone doesn’t have top-of-the-line features like the phones ranked higher in our comparison. However, it is easy to use and comes with comprehensive customer support. This phone is the ideal option for the elderly and hard of hearing. If you don’t need a lot of features or advanced functionality, the E814CC is a good choice."]},"id":"c5403bba-8ad1-4ff6-a551-5bb3b65df3a5","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_69657","url":"/clarity-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"rebecca-armstrong","url":"/author/rebecca-armstrong","dateCreated":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","name":"Rebecca Armstrong","dateModified":"2019-04-16T16:01:12Z","id":"6pCy2z6qSDBXrw3J9gsMqa","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2017-10-11T13:37:33Z","datePublished":"2017-10-11T13:37:33Z","name":"Clarity E814CC","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side-by-side comparison because it has been discontinued.","review":{"rating":67,"verdict":"The Clarity E814CC comes with an arsenal of volume boosting options and most of the basic features. It is a great option for anyone who&#8217;s hard of hearing.","pros":["It can amplify audio up to 40 decibels."],"cons":["It lacks a few basic features, like background noise reduction."]},"strapline":"Editor’s Note: This product has been removed from our side